anguage.svg.png" data-file-width="130" data-file-height="200" data-file-type="drawing" height="308" width="200" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/97/Chineselanguage.svg/400px-Chineselanguage.svg.png 2x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/97/Chineselanguage.svg/300px-Chineselanguage.svg.png 1.5x"/></a></figure-inline><div>Hànyǔ (<i>Chinese</i>) written in <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Traditional_Chinese_characters" title="Traditional Chinese characters">traditional</a> (top), <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Simplified_Chinese_characters" title="Simplified Chinese characters">simplified</a> (middle) characters and alternative name (bottom)</div></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="padding-top:0.225em;line-height:1.1em; padding-right:0.5em;">Native<span typeof="mw:Entity"> </span>to</th><td style="line-height:1.35em;"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./China" title="China">People's Republic of China</a>, <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Taiwan" title="Taiwan">Republic of China (Taiwan)</a></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="padding-top:0.225em;line-height:1.1em; padding-right:0.5em;">Ethnicity</th><td style="line-height:1.35em;"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Han_Chinese" title="Han Chinese">Han Chinese</a></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="padding-top:0.225em;line-height:1.1em; padding-right:0.5em;"><div style="padding:0.1em 0;line-height:1.2em;">Native speakers</div></th><td style="line-height:1.35em;">1.2 billion<span typeof="mw:Entity"> </span>(2004)<sup about="#mwt429" class="mw-ref" id="cite_ref-FOOTNOTEChinese_Academy_of_Social_Sciences20123_1-0" rel="dc:references" typeof="mw:Extension/ref" data-mw='{"name":"ref","attrs":{"name":"FOOTNOTEChinese Academy of Social Sciences20123"},"body":{"id":"mw-reference-text-cite_note-FOOTNOTEChinese_Academy_of_Social_Sciences20123-1"}}'><a href="./Chinese_language#cite_note-FOOTNOTEChinese_Academy_of_Social_Sciences20123-1" style="counter-reset: mw-Ref 1;"><span class="mw-reflink-text">[1]</span></a>