</div></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="padding-top:0.225em;line-height:1.1em; padding-right:0.5em;"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./List_of_language_regulators" title="List of language regulators">Regulated<span typeof="mw:Entity"> </span>by</a></th><td style="line-height:1.35em;">National Commission on Language and Script Work (Mainland China)<sup about="#mwt824" class="mw-ref" id="cite_ref-2" rel="dc:references" typeof="mw:Extension/ref" data-mw='{"name":"ref","attrs":{},"body":{"id":"mw-reference-text-cite_note-2"}}'><a href="./Chinese_language#cite_note-2" style="counter-reset: mw-Ref 2;"><span class="mw-reflink-text">[2]</span></a></sup><br/><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./National_Languages_Committee" title="National Languages Committee">National Languages Committee</a> (Taiwan)<br/><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Civil_Service_Bureau" title="Civil Service Bureau">Civil Service Bureau</a> (Hong Kong)<br/><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Promote_Mandarin_Council" title="Promote Mandarin Council">Promote Mandarin Council</a> (Singapore)<br/><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Chinese_Language_Standardisation_Council_of_Malaysia" title="Chinese Language Standardisation Council of Malaysia">Chinese Language Standardisation Council</a> (Malaysia)</td></tr><tr><th colspan="2" style="text-align:center;color: black; background-color: salmon;">Language codes</th></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="padding-top:0.225em;line-height:1.1em; padding-right:0.5em;"><span class="nowrap"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./ISO_639-1" title="ISO 639-1">ISO 639-1</a></span></th><td style="line-height:1.35em;"><code><span class="plainlinks"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://www.loc.gov/standards/iso639-2/php/langcodes_name.php?iso_639_1=zh">zh</a></span></code></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="padding-top:0.225em;line-height:1.1em; padding-right:0.5em;"><span class="nowrap"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./ISO_639-2" title="ISO 639-2">ISO 639-2</a></span></th><td style="line-height:1.35e