yǔ</span></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="font-weight:normal;"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Yale_romanization_of_Mandarin" title="Yale romanization of Mandarin">Yale Romanization</a></th><td><span style="font-style:normal" lang="zh-Latn" title="Chinese-language transliteration">Hàn-yǔ</span></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="font-weight:normal;"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Help:IPA/Mandarin" title="Help:IPA/Mandarin">IPA</a></th><td><span style="font-style:normal" lang="zh-Latn" title="Chinese-language transliteration"><span class="IPA" style="white-space:nowrap"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Help:IPA/Mandarin" title="Help:IPA/Mandarin">[xa<span typeof="mw:Entity">̂</span>n.y<span typeof="mw:Entity">̀</span>]</a></span></span></td></tr><tr><th colspan="2" style="text-align:center;background-color: #dcffc9;"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Wu_Chinese" title="Wu Chinese">Wu</a></th></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="font-weight:normal;">Romanization</th><td><span style="font-style:normal" lang="wuu-Latn" title="Wu Chinese-language transliteration">hoe3 nyiu2</span></td></tr><tr><th colspan="2" style="text-align:center;background-color: #dcffc9;"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Hakka_Chinese" title="Hakka Chinese">Hakka</a></th></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="font-weight:normal;"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Guangdong_Romanization#Hakka" title="Guangdong Romanization">Romanization</a></th><td><span style="font-style:normal" lang="hak-Latn" title="Hakka-language transliteration">Hon Ngi</span></td></tr><tr><th colspan="2" style="text-align:center;background-color: #dcffc9;"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Cantonese" title="Cantonese">Yue: Cantonese</a></th></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="font-weight:normal;"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Yale_romanization_of_Cantonese" title="Yale romanization of Cantonese">Yale Romanization</a></th><td><span style="font-style:normal" lang="yue-Latn" title="Yue Chinese-language transliteration">hon yúh</span></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style