<p id="mwAc8">Standard <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Cantonese" title="Cantonese" id="mwAdA">Cantonese</a>, in contrast, has six tones in open syllables and three tones in syllables ending with stops:<sup about="#mwt139" class="mw-ref" id="cite_ref-FOOTNOTEMatthewsYip199420–22_73-0" rel="dc:references" typeof="mw:Transclusion  mw:Extension/ref" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"sfnp","href":"./Template:Sfnp"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"Matthews"},"2":{"wt":"Yip"},"3":{"wt":"1994"},"pp":{"wt":"20–22"}},"i":0}}]}'><a href="./Chinese_language#cite_note-FOOTNOTEMatthewsYip199420–22-73" style="counter-reset: mw-Ref 70;"><span class="mw-reflink-text">[70]</span></a></sup></p>
<table class="wikitable" id="mwAdE">
<caption id="mwAdI">Example of Standard Cantonese tones</caption>
<tbody id="mwAdM"><tr id="mwAdQ"><th id="mwAdU">Characters</th>
<th id="mwAdY"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Jyutping" title="Jyutping" id="mwAdc">Jyutping</a></th>
<th id="mwAdg">Pitch contour</th>
<th id="mwAdk">Meaning</th></tr>
<tr id="mwAdo">
<td id="mwAds"><span lang="zh-Hans" title="Chinese language text" about="#mwt140" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"lang","href":"./Template:Lang"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"zh-Hans"},"2":{"wt":"[[wiktionary:诗|诗]]"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAdw"><a rel="mw:WikiLink/Interwiki" href="https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/诗" title="wiktionary:诗">诗</a></span><link rel="mw:PageProp/Category" href="./Category:Articles_containing_Chinese-language_text" about="#mwt140" id="mwAd0"/>/<span lang="zh-Hant" title="Chinese language text" about="#mwt141" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"lang","href":"./Template:Lang"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"zh-Hant"},"2":{"wt":"[[wiktionary:詩|詩]]"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAd4"><a rel="mw:WikiLink/Interwiki" href="https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/詩" title="wiktionary:詩">詩</a></span><link rel="mw:PageProp/Category" href="./Category:Articles_containing_Chinese-language_text" about="#mwt141" id="mwAd8"/></td>
